  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为FinTech_PaymentGateway设计一个状态流转图，核心是处理支付网关的授权令牌生命周期。从IDLE状态开始，触发Kick-off事件后进入FETCH阶段拉取令牌。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "Kick-off"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，IDLE作为初始状态，Kick-off触发FETCH。FETCH完成后进入PARSE解析令牌对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，PARSE这里要分叉：Valid的话走ARB_READ进行仲裁读权限，Invalid直接进ERROR状态。ERROR最终要通过SW clear回到IDLE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "Valid",
        "Invalid",
        "SW clear"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加PARSE到ARB_READ的Valid分支，以及PARSE到ERROR的Invalid分支。继续补充ARB_READ之后的流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ARB_READ获得Grant后进入READ，READ完成再到ARB_WRITE仲裁写权限，Grant之后进入WRITE。注意这里Complete和Grant的触发条件不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "Grant",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：READ到ARB_WRITE是Complete触发，但ARB_READ到READ是Grant触发？这两个仲裁状态的命名容易混淆，需要区分清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "Grant",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，ARB_READ和ARB_WRITE分别控制读写仲裁。WRITE完成后进入CHAIN状态，这里要处理链式调用：如果不是最后一条就Next回到FETCH，是最后一条则进入COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE",
        "Next",
        "Last"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加WRITE到CHAIN的Complete流转，以及CHAIN的两个出口。最后COMPLETE通过IRQ sent回到IDLE，ERROR通过SW clear回到IDLE，这样整个闭环就完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
